===Pronunciation===
*ἀκάθαρτος / akathartos / ak-ath'-ar-tos

=== Etymology ===

*From [[α]]- {{GG|1}} (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of [[καθαίρω]] ({{GG|2508}}) (meaning cleansed); impure (ceremonially, morally (lewd) or specifically (demonic)): 
=== Adjective ===
[[foul]], [[unclean]].